PROCEDURE BuildNameList :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

  DEFINE INPUT  PARAMETER p_Objects  AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
  DEFINE OUTPUT PARAMETER p_NameList AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
  
