  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
-------------------------------------------------------------*/

  DEFINE INPUT PARAMETER p_State    AS CHARACTER    NO-UNDO.

  DEFINE VARIABLE Ret_Val           AS LOGICAL      NO-UNDO.
  
  DO WITH FRAME {&FRAME-NAME} :
    CASE p_State :
    
        WHEN Type_Proc THEN
        DO:
            ASSIGN Type:SCREEN-VALUE    = Type_Proc.
            CASE Name:SCREEN-VALUE:
